
#### What Will I Learn?
- You will learn how to use Inkscape to draw a cartoon image.

#### Requirements
Inkscape
(What is Inkscape?
Inkscape is professional quality vector graphics software which runs on Windows, Mac OS X and GNU/Linux. It is used by design professionals and hobbyists worldwide, for creating a wide variety of graphics such as illustrations, icons, logos, diagrams, maps and web graphics. Inkscape uses the W3C open standard SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics) as its native format, and is free and open-source software.)
You can download it here：https://inkscape.org

#### Difficulty
- Basic


#### Tutorial Contents
First install inkscape.
You can download it here：https://inkscape.org
and open it

You will learn how to use Inkscape to draw a cartoon image.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs16.jpg)


1. Using a circular tool, shortcut key (F5),Draw 3 circles.

![qs01.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs01.jpg)

2. Moving small circle.To the right place.

![qs02.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs02.jpg)

3. Color to the circle

![qs03.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs03.jpg)

4. use Bezier Curves,shortcut key (shift+F6),Draw hair.

![qs04.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs04.jpg)

5. Finish the hair.

![qs05.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs05.jpg)

6. Using a circular tool, shortcut key (F5),Draw 2 circles.This is the eye.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs06.jpg)

7. Using a rectangle tool, shortcut key (F4),Draw eyebrows.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs07.jpg)

8. Double hit the eyebrows,rotate it.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs08.jpg)

9. Ctrl+D,copy,and mirror

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs09.jpg)

10. complete

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs10.jpg)

11. use Bezier Curves,shortcut key (shift+F6),Draw mouth.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs11.jpg)

12. Shift+Ctrl+F,advanced setting,Set the stroke.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs12.jpg)

13. Round angle

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs13.jpg)

14. Using a circular tool, shortcut key (F5),Draw 2 circles.This is the blush.

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs14.jpg)

15. Color to the circle

![qs03.jpg](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs15.jpg)

16. complete

![](https://github.com/maiyude2018/Inkscape/blob/master/image/qs16.jpg)

